snippet.title: Khodam: The Contract Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Khodam is a First person game that was inspired by the folklore from Indonesia about an invisible protective figure or Khodam. Player will play as Dara who is a streamer that is searching for her identity. Feeling from the aura of the destiny line that trapped Dara into the cursed road is an experience of fear and intriguing to follow.
#KhodamTheContract #Khodam #Indonesia
